---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import PrivateHeader from "../../components/PrivateHeader.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout noindex={true} title="Getting Started | Leigh-Ann Martin" description="Step-by-step action plan for your career launch.">
  <PrivateHeader />
  <div class="md:ml-60">
  <main>
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="bg-primary pt-24 pb-12 md:pt-16 md:pb-16">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-secondary mb-4">Action Plan</p>
        <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl text-white leading-tight mb-4">
          Getting Started
        </h1>
        <p class="text-white/50 text-base leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto mb-6">
          Your pipeline is working. 14-23% resume-to-interview conversion is strong. The gap is closing interviews, not getting them. This plan fixes that while building your fractional business in parallel.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-2">
          <span class="bg-white/10 border border-white/10 text-white/60 text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full">2 parallel tracks</span>
          <span class="bg-white/10 border border-white/10 text-white/60 text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full">4-week phased plan</span>
          <span class="bg-white/10 border border-white/10 text-white/60 text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded-full">DM + outreach strategy</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Two Tracks -->
    <section class="py-10 bg-warm border-b border-primary/[0.06]">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border-l-4 border-l-secondary">
            <p class="text-secondary text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase mb-2">Track 1: Corporate</p>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-lg text-primary mb-2">Full-time EA role ($120K-$165K)</h3>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Apply to live postings, register with recruiters, close interviews by fixing delivery (conciseness) and positioning (strategic partner, not flight risk).</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border-l-4 border-l-primary/30">
            <p class="text-primary/60 text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase mb-2">Track 2: Fractional</p>
            <h3 class="font-serif text-lg text-primary mb-2">Fractional EA practice (outcome-based)</h3>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Prospect outreach to funded companies, LinkedIn positioning, case-study-driven pitching. Use the website as your proof of credibility.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-xs text-center mt-4 italic">Run both tracks simultaneously. Whichever hits first, you're ready.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- WEEK 1: Days 1-3 -->
    <section class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-cream">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-secondary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-serif text-lg font-bold flex-shrink-0">1</div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-secondary text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase">This Week: Days 1-3</p>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-primary">Fix the Close</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed">Your pipeline is healthy. The problem is interview delivery. Before you apply to anything new, sharpen the tools that will close the deal.</p>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 accent-secondary w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-primary text-sm">Read your Competitive Edge + Objections sections</p>
                <p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">Internalize your 7 differentiators and the counter-strategies for "long-winded," "flight risk," and "cannabis stigma." These are the three things costing you offers.</p>
                <a href={`${base}private/interview-prep#competitive-edge`} class="text-secondary text-xs font-medium mt-1 inline-block hover:underline">Go to Interview Prep &rarr;</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 accent-secondary w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-primary text-sm">Practice "Tell Me About Yourself" out loud, 5 times</p>
                <p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">Set a timer. It should land under 60 seconds. Use the Present-Past-Future format. Record yourself on the 5th attempt and listen back. If it sounds conversational and confident, you're ready.</p>
                <a href={`${base}private/interview-prep#playbook`} class="text-secondary text-xs font-medium mt-1 inline-block hover:underline">See your script &rarr;</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 accent-secondary w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-primary text-sm">Pick 3-4 STAR stories to have ready</p>
                <p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">You have 7 stories pre-built. Pick the ones that cover: board prep under pressure, investor relations at scale, anticipating executive needs, and improving a process. Those 4 cover 90% of interview questions.</p>
                <a href={`${base}private/interview-prep#star-stories`} class="text-secondary text-xs font-medium mt-1 inline-block hover:underline">Review STAR stories &rarr;</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 accent-secondary w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-primary text-sm">Send all 7 LinkedIn recommendation requests</p>
                <p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">Each email is pre-drafted with a sample recommendation and a direct link to the LinkedIn form. Click the "Draft Email" button for each contact. Takes 10 minutes total.</p>
                <a href={`${base}private/recommendations`} class="text-secondary text-xs font-medium mt-1 inline-block hover:underline">Go to Recommendations &rarr;</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 accent-secondary w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-primary text-sm">Register with 2 Tier 1 recruiter agencies</p>
                <p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">Start with <strong>C-Suite Assistants</strong> (6,000+ NYC EA database, gold standard) and <strong>Glocap Search</strong> (hedge fund and PE specialization, 750K+ candidate database).</p>
                <a href={`${base}private/opportunities`} class="text-secondary text-xs font-medium mt-1 inline-block hover:underline">See recruiter list &rarr;</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- WEEK 1: Days 4-7 -->
    <section class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-warm">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-secondary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-serif text-lg font-bold flex-shrink-0">2</div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-secondary text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase">This Week: Days 4-7</p>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-primary">Activate Both Pipelines</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border-l-4 border-l-secondary">
            <p class="text-secondary text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider uppercase mb-2">Corporate Track</p>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 accent-secondary w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-primary text-sm">Apply to all 6 Priority A jobs</p>
                <p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">Top targets: <strong>Alger</strong> ($125K-$175K, asset management CEO/CIO), <strong>Rimes Technologies</strong> ($125K-$145K, fintech CEO ex-Goldman), <strong>Point72</strong> ($100K-$130K+ bonus, hedge fund). Tailor your cover letter using the strategy notes on each listing.</p>
                <a href={`${base}private/opportunities`} class="text-secondary text-xs font-medium mt-1 inline-block hover:underline">Go to Opportunities &rarr;</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm border-l-4 border-l-primary/30">
            <p class="text-primary/60 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider uppercase mb-2">Fractional Track</p>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 accent-secondary w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-primary text-sm">Send 5 fractional EA prospecting emails</p>
                <p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">Start with Priority A prospects. Each email is click-to-draft: <strong>Kim Seth</strong> (Nilo, $101M raise), <strong>Bing Yuan</strong> (OnCusp, IND approval), <strong>Jason Brouwer</strong> (Proxima, $80M), <strong>Gabe Stengel</strong> (Rogo, $750M valuation), <strong>Farooq Malik</strong> (Rain, unicorn).</p>
                <a href={`${base}private/outreach`} class="text-secondary text-xs font-medium mt-1 inline-block hover:underline">Go to Outreach Emails &rarr;</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 accent-secondary w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-primary text-sm">Send warm reconnection emails to former employers</p>
                <p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">Pre-written warm emails for <strong>Eric Venker</strong> (new Immunovant CEO) and <strong>John Hartmann</strong> (former Ascend CEO). These are your highest-probability leads because you have institutional knowledge.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 accent-secondary w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-primary text-sm">Review your public website</p>
                <p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">Walk through it as a prospect CEO who just got your email. Does it tell your story? Anything to change before prospects start clicking through?</p>
                <a href={base} class="text-secondary text-xs font-medium mt-1 inline-block hover:underline">View public site &rarr;</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- WEEK 2 -->
    <section class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-cream">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-secondary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-serif text-lg font-bold flex-shrink-0">3</div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-secondary text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase">Week 2</p>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-primary">Follow Up + Expand</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 accent-secondary w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-primary text-sm">Follow up on all Week 1 outreach (Day 5-7 after sending)</p>
                <p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">"Hi [Name], just bumping this in case it got buried. Happy to chat for 15 minutes if the timing makes sense." No new pitch. Just a nudge.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 accent-secondary w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-primary text-sm">Register with 2 more Tier 1 recruiters</p>
                <p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1"><strong>BCL Search</strong> (premium finance EAs, $200K-$275K roles) and <strong>Right Hand Talent</strong> (Chief of Staff specialists, founded by a former CoS).</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 accent-secondary w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-primary text-sm">Send next 5 outreach emails (Priority B prospects)</p>
                <p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">Continue through the outreach list. Each email is already customized. You're building a pipeline, not waiting for one response.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 accent-secondary w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-primary text-sm">Apply to Priority B jobs</p>
                <p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">Earnest, Addepar, Via Transportation, GlossGenius. Below target salary but strong companies with equity upside or good brand value.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 accent-secondary w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" />
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-primary text-sm">Practice the hardest objections out loud</p>
                <p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">Set a timer. Under 60 seconds each: "Why are you leaving?" "Where do you see yourself in 5 years?" "Why EA and not Chief of Staff?" "Tell me about a difficult executive." Conversational, not rehearsed.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- WEEK 3-4 -->
    <section class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-warm">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-secondary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-serif text-lg font-bold flex-shrink-0">4</div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-secondary text-xs font-bold tracking-wider uppercase">Weeks 3-4</p>
            <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-primary">Double Down on What's Working</h2>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 accent-secondary w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" />
              <p class="font-medium text-primary text-sm">Check which outreach emails got replies. Send personalized follow-ups to responders. Archive non-responders for 30-day re-engagement.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 accent-secondary w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" />
              <p class="font-medium text-primary text-sm">Monitor the 8 funded companies for new EA/CoS job postings (check careers pages weekly).</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 accent-secondary w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" />
              <p class="font-medium text-primary text-sm">Register with Tier 2 recruiter agencies (Pocketbook Agency, Beacon Hill, A-List Associates, Career Group, Silver Chair Partners).</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 accent-secondary w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" />
              <p class="font-medium text-primary text-sm">If fractional conversations are progressing, send your website link + services page as a leave-behind after discovery calls.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <input type="checkbox" class="mt-1 accent-secondary w-4 h-4 flex-shrink-0" />
              <p class="font-medium text-primary text-sm">Adjust positioning based on interview feedback. If you keep hearing the same objection, revisit the counter-strategy and refine your delivery.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- DM & OUTREACH PIPELINE STRATEGY -->
    <section class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-cream">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 12h.01M12 12h.01M16 12h.01M21 12c0 4.418-4.03 8-9 8a9.863 9.863 0 01-4.255-.949L3 20l1.395-3.72C3.512 15.042 3 13.574 3 12c0-4.418 4.03-8 9-8s9 3.582 9 8z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-primary">LinkedIn DM & Outreach Pipeline</h2>
        </div>

        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mb-6 leading-relaxed">Cold email is your primary outreach channel. LinkedIn DMs are the follow-up and relationship layer. Here's how to use both together.</p>

        <h3 class="font-semibold text-primary text-base mb-3">LinkedIn DM Templates</h3>
        <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-secondary text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider uppercase mb-2">Connection Request (CEO you've emailed)</p>
            <div class="bg-cream rounded-lg p-4 text-sm text-text/80 leading-relaxed">
              <p>Hi [Name], I sent you a note last week about fractional executive operations support. I've spent 5 years supporting a biotech CEO through clinical transitions and board governance. Would love to connect and share a bit more about how I work. No pitch, just context.</p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-2 italic">Send 2-3 days after your cold email. If they accept, wait 24 hours before messaging.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-secondary text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider uppercase mb-2">Follow-up DM (after connection accepted)</p>
            <div class="bg-cream rounded-lg p-4 text-sm text-text/80 leading-relaxed">
              <p>Thanks for connecting, [Name]. I noticed [specific thing about their company, e.g., "the Series A announcement" or "the new board member"]. I've handled exactly that kind of operational complexity before. If you're ever curious about fractional EA support, I'm an open book. Here's a quick look at my background: [website link]</p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-2 italic">Always reference something specific. Generic DMs get ignored.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-secondary text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider uppercase mb-2">Warm reconnection (former colleagues)</p>
            <div class="bg-cream rounded-lg p-4 text-sm text-text/80 leading-relaxed">
              <p>Hi [Name], it's been a while. I've been building a fractional executive support practice since leaving [company]. I'd love to reconnect and hear what you're working on. Open to a quick call this week?</p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-2 italic">Use for former colleagues at Immunovant, Ascend, PwC, Third Bridge. Your network is warmer than you think.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-secondary text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider uppercase mb-2">EA/CoS peer outreach (backdoor referrals)</p>
            <div class="bg-cream rounded-lg p-4 text-sm text-text/80 leading-relaxed">
              <p>Hi [Name], I came across your profile. I'm a senior EA with 12+ years across biotech, finance, and publicly traded companies. I'm exploring new opportunities and noticed you support [CEO name]. I'd love to learn about your experience at [company]. Always great to connect with fellow EAs who operate at a strategic level.</p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-2 italic">EAs often know when their company is hiring before the posting goes live. This is how you get referred internally.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3 class="font-semibold text-primary text-base mb-3">Follow-Up Cadence</h3>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm mb-8">
          <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-secondary font-bold text-sm mt-0.5 w-16 flex-shrink-0">Day 1</span>
              <p class="text-text-muted">Send cold email (from the Outreach page).</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-secondary font-bold text-sm mt-0.5 w-16 flex-shrink-0">Day 3</span>
              <p class="text-text-muted">Send LinkedIn connection request with the short note above.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-secondary font-bold text-sm mt-0.5 w-16 flex-shrink-0">Day 7</span>
              <p class="text-text-muted">Email follow-up: "Hi [Name], just bumping this in case it got buried. Happy to chat for 15 minutes if the timing makes sense."</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-secondary font-bold text-sm mt-0.5 w-16 flex-shrink-0">Day 14</span>
              <p class="text-text-muted">If connected on LinkedIn but no reply: send the follow-up DM with a specific reference to their company news.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-secondary font-bold text-sm mt-0.5 w-16 flex-shrink-0">Day 30</span>
              <p class="text-text-muted">"No worries if the timing isn't right. I'll keep an eye on [company] and reach out if something changes." Then archive. Don't chase.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h3 class="font-semibold text-primary text-base mb-3">Pipeline Tracker</h3>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mb-4">Create a simple spreadsheet or Notion table with these columns:</p>
          <div class="overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full text-xs">
              <thead>
                <tr class="border-b border-primary/10">
                  <th class="text-left py-2 pr-2 font-semibold text-primary">Company</th>
                  <th class="text-left py-2 px-2 font-semibold text-primary">Contact</th>
                  <th class="text-left py-2 px-2 font-semibold text-primary">Track</th>
                  <th class="text-left py-2 px-2 font-semibold text-primary">Status</th>
                  <th class="text-left py-2 px-2 font-semibold text-primary">Last Action</th>
                  <th class="text-left py-2 pl-2 font-semibold text-primary">Next Step</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody class="text-text-muted">
                <tr class="border-b border-primary/[0.04]"><td class="py-2 pr-2">Alger</td><td class="py-2 px-2">HR/Recruiter</td><td class="py-2 px-2">Corporate</td><td class="py-2 px-2 text-secondary font-medium">Applied</td><td class="py-2 px-2">Apr 15</td><td class="py-2 pl-2">Follow up Apr 22</td></tr>
                <tr class="border-b border-primary/[0.04]"><td class="py-2 pr-2">Nilo Therapeutics</td><td class="py-2 px-2">Kim Seth (CEO)</td><td class="py-2 px-2">Fractional</td><td class="py-2 px-2 text-secondary font-medium">Email sent</td><td class="py-2 px-2">Apr 16</td><td class="py-2 pl-2">LinkedIn connect Apr 18</td></tr>
